<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id912b2a00-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id912b2a01-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The Iran Sanctions Act of 1996, referred to in par. (8), is <ref href="/us/pl/104/172">Pub. L. 104–172</ref>, <date date="1996-08-05">Aug. 5, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1541">110 Stat. 1541</ref>, which is set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t50/s1701">section 1701 of Title 50</ref>, War and National Defense.</p>
</note>
</notes>
